Maxted appointed chief exec at Chesterfield . UK real estate group Chesterfield Properties Plc said on Friday that Robert Maxted has been appointed chief executive following the completion of the acquisition of Albion Property Investments Ltd . Maxted was chief executive of Albion and the move allows Chesterfield chairman and chief executive Roger Wingate to concentrate solely on the role of chairman . Chesterfield bought Albion for 21 . 9 million stg . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 4019 
